headline: GTA Online
subtitle: On the Podium This Week: Coil Brawler
content: Swing by the lobby of The Diamond Casino & Resort to give the Lucky Wheel a spin for the opportunity to walk away with GTA$, RP, or all sorts of mystery prizes. This week on the podium is the Coil Brawler, an off-roader with enough horsepower under the hood to muscle its way over even the toughest terrain.
